{"tid":1785001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警查野餐街坊 放生噪音大媽","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T05:52:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6419fbc72ac34e3f75c64b6ec2866f127c33de1f","tid":1785001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/LLOIGCM7L6T2O6TZE6XJQEYFFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FLLOIGCM7L6T2O6TZE6XJQEYFFM%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7q3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=a53ad0fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FLLOIGCM7L6T2O6TZE6XJQEYFFM%2F&h=a44f1c8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/LLOIGCM7L6T2O6TZE6XJQEYFFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n警查野餐街坊 放生噪音大媽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】屯門公園大媽檔噪音問題死灰復燃，約50名街坊昨響應網上號召到場「野餐」，其間與大媽及一批大媽粉絲對罵。大批防暴警趕到截查街坊，卻「放生」大媽，惹來市民指摘徇私枉法。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：市民籲罷食藍店：一啖一滴細路血<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191216/large/1576425930_6513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576425930_6513.jpg&h=a820ec0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【屯門】一名紅裙大媽現身屯門公園，有市民遞上10元紙幣諷刺其以賣藝為名收錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一大媽拒出示身份證<br />\n<br />\n昨午3時許，約50名市民到屯門公園「野餐」，發起活動的屯門區工黨候任區議員林明恩和林健翔，在場向康文署職員投訴大媽噪音，職員向數個大媽檔發警告。一名穿灰衫花裙大媽拒出示身份證，阻礙職員發傳票，數名軍裝警到場處理，但涉事大媽卻乘亂離開。人群繼續狙擊其他唱歌大媽，更與大媽粉絲對罵。<br />\n<br />\n未幾一名身穿紅裙大媽現身，向粉絲派食物，有市民遞上10元紙幣，詢問可否「摸手仔」，迫使她避走洗手間，由一名老翁協助逃走。至下午5時許，約50名防暴到公園截查市民，之後收隊離開，但因在場街坊歡呼揮手，聲稱有人起哄又折返。<br />\n<br />\n一名中年女子質問防暴警是否記得入職誓言，被警察要求出示身份證，在旁一名男子不齒警察所為，展示一塊寫上「警察誓詞 不畏懼 不徇私 不對他人懷惡意 不敵視他人」白布，並向警察大聲朗讀，事件中無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者邵靖妍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191216/large/1576425928_0d72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576425928_0d72.jpg&h=6eff8030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【屯門】防暴到場截查市民，對多名年輕人搜身。"},{"pid":"f2cfcaff160a85b4baaa34e26f05483ba673b444","tid":1785001,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja88Na2.jpg&h=543efee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRJ7hx.jpg&h=a821da85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咤叱歌曲投票link 👇👇👇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://usca.my903.com/mobile/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com%2Fmobile%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7q3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=0cc18fce\" target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com/mobile/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkEv0ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkEv0ur.jpg&h=03b9c910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db3f7ba5c1176274785dbcdd513108f18f7de29a","tid":1785001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boyz9mA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fboyz9mA.jpg&h=681d4c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpGueC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpGueC9.jpg&h=2c51b16f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"808645bba9f0a7626b9abc70dfb24c2c418f0249","tid":1785001,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"只要企係香港市民對立面既事情 黑警都會做"},{"pid":"7eeb9002de88c4e60b4bfc57b8d6cc19ec0542c6","tid":1785001,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:31:34.000Z","msg":"其實d警察幪面係哋已經係制服嘅一部份 <br />\n<br />\n行咇都可以幪"},{"pid":"c56d33b1432b8aa9848c4da8179db42cd151ce71","tid":1785001,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eeb9002de88c4e60b4bfc57b8d6cc19ec0542c6","tid":1785001,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:31:34.000Z","msg":"其實d警察幪面係哋已經係制服嘅一部份 <br />\n<br />\n行咇都可以幪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"敢出樣咩佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}